{"tid":1319521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"決定不向民主黨提供捐獻","createTime":"2019-07-15T07:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:58:22.000Z","uid":268359,"like":11,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1729cdba3c8f7adfa420d04fdf2b7f6f4f18d42b","tid":1319521,"uid":268359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n一直以為民主黨建設民主中國，以溫和路線迎難而上爭取民主，本已決定將港幣__元積蓄捐獻於民主黨協助其工作事務。直至7月14日，我從何君堯議員的臉書貼文發現原來民主黨收取六千萬進行革命，這種非法行為與建設民主中國的目標相違，反映民主黨謊話連篇，以及民主黨財源廣進，不需本人捐獻。因此我將收回捐獻決定。<br />\n<br />\n（如在以後有關法律訴訟（包括誹謗）上需要本人協助，本人不介意提供協助。）<br />\n<br />\nXXX<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBqMMYU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBqMMYU.png&h=c7eaee14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3101c086f20771ee8089b9eabaac06c2847cf737","tid":1319521,"uid":268359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"你諗清楚我做緊咩先負皮<br />\n助攻呀宜家"},{"pid":"c691f4e9e648bf89b7d9f557576938f778926247","tid":1319521,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw真係好易引負皮"},{"pid":"db23cc969cf06d2b4c8a93651a261fd723d08825","tid":1319521,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:37:20.000Z","msg":"玩大佢"},{"pid":"2c52c3438c481f7013129f7fcf589fee125c3bfd","tid":1319521,"uid":268359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"你諗下點搞何妖？<br />\n<br />\n誹謗 要  <br />\n1 有關事情具有誹謗意思；   <span style=\"color: blue;\">（非法性質）</span><br />\n2 該事情已向第三者傳達；及  <span style=\"color: blue;\"> （？）</span><br />\n3 該事情是針對某個人   <span style=\"color: blue;\">（開左名）</span><br />\n同埋有實質損失。   （？）<br />\n<br />\n